The '''123rd Nightstalker Group''' was an [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Starfleet]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] [[Fighter wing/Legends|wing]] that participated in combat operations during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. Comprised wholly of [[TIE/ln space superiority starfighter/Legends|TIE Fighters]], the wing was stationed aboard ''[[Singularity]]'' and served under the direct command of [[Cronal|Blackhole]].<ref name="tep">{{GamerCite|5|The Emperor's Pawns}}</ref>

